name: Emptiness
description:
This is my henesis in the Tezosverse as Sans Stroke. 

The beginning of this introspective manifesto goes along the meaning of my concept and style in art. For a long time I’ve tried to define myself and asked how other people started. Since everything may be a remix, I’ll just try to use this as an excuse to start this journey. 

Without any further, the object in the middle is me, distorted and empty in ideas but not in creativity, launching myself into this project without strokes. 

@tdanyrus
